# VibOS Comp Delivery Infrastructure

## Purpose

Delivery infrastructure makes the MVP buildable, deployable, observable, manageable, secure, and reversible. It prevents a working local app from being mistaken for a serious enterprise MVP.

## Core Question

Can the system be built, checked, deployed, observed, diagnosed, and rolled back through repeatable code or documented commands?

