## Required Pipeline Controls

- tests, lint, type checks, or equivalent quality checks
- dependency and security checks
- build or artifact generation
- environment and secrets inventory
- deploy command or deployment-as-code
- health and smoke check after deployment or local proof substitute
- logs, request IDs, metrics/traces, or error reporting sufficient to diagnose the core workflow
- rollback, redeploy, or recovery note

## Blocking Rule

For VibOS Comp, delivery infrastructure blocks completion if CI/CD, deployment, environment/secrets, observability, smoke/health, rollback, or runbook evidence is missing or purely aspirational.
